{"product_id":"al-saalim-premium-attar-combo-pack-pack-of-3-shanaya-sadaf-ameerul-oud-roll-on-6ml-each-alcohol-free","title":"Al-Saalim Premium Attar Combo Pack (Pack of 3 – Shanaya, Sadaf \u0026 Ameerul Oud) | Roll On 6ml Each | Alcohol Free","description":"\u003cp\u003eExperience the luxury of multiple signature fragrances with the Al-Saalim Premium Attar Combo Pack. This exclusive set includes three elegant and long-lasting attars — Shanaya, Sadaf, and Ameerul Oud, carefully crafted to offer a perfect variety of fragrance styles.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEach attar in this combo is alcohol-free, skin-friendly, and designed to deliver a rich and lasting aroma suitable for different moods and occasions. Whether you prefer soft floral notes, fresh elegant scents, or deep oud fragrances, this combo offers the perfect balance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pack is ideal for personal use, gifting, or exploring multiple premium fragrances in one set.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCombo Includes\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e✔ Shanaya Attar – Soft, sweet \u0026amp; floral fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e✔ Sadaf Attar – Fresh, smooth \u0026amp; elegant aroma\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e✔ Ameerul Oud Attar – Rich, woody \u0026amp; royal oud fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePack of 3 Premium Attars\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6ml Each Bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol Free \u0026amp; Skin Friendly\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong Lasting Fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLuxury Roll-On Glass Bottles\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for Men \u0026amp; Women\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePerfect for Daily Wear \u0026amp; Special Occasions\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIdeal Gift Set\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy Choose This Combo\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMultiple fragrance options in one pack\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium quality traditional attars\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp